{
  "openapi": "3.0.1",
  "info": {
    "title": "文档服务 API",
    "description": "WisePen 文档上传、解析、转换与详情接口",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://172.28.0.29:19906",
      "description": "Generated server url"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "文档处理",
      "description": "文档上传、处理状态、预览与信息查询"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/document/uploadDoc": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["文档处理"],
        "summary": "初始化文档上传",
        "description": "- 用途：为当前用户创建文档上传任务，并申请对象存储直传凭证。\n- 请求：filename 为展示文件名；extension 为文件扩展名；md5 用于秒传判定；expectedSize 为预期文件大小。\n- 约束：当前用户必须已登录；扩展名必须属于文档服务支持的文件类型；请求字段必须通过校验。\n- 处理：生成 documentId，向文件存储服务申请上传 URL 或触发秒传；保存文档上传元信息。命中秒传时立即发布文档解析任务；未命中秒传时不直接接收文件内容。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN；文件类型不支持 -> DocumentError.CANNOT_SUPPORT_FILE_TYPE；存储服务申请上传凭证失败 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_UPLOAD_URL_APPLY_FAILED。\n- 响应：返回 documentId、objectKey、上传凭证信息和是否秒传。\n",
        "operationId": "uploadDoc",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentUploadInitRequest"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RDocumentUploadInitResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/document/syncDocStatus": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["文档处理"],
        "summary": "刷新文档状态",
        "description": "- 用途：主动同步当前用户上传文档的最新处理状态。\n- 请求：documentId 指定待刷新的文档任务。\n- 约束：当前用户必须是该文档上传者；目标文档必须存在。\n- 处理：如果文档仍处于 UPLOADING，会查询文件存储记录；确认上传完成后更新为 UPLOADED 并发布解析任务。非 UPLOADING 状态仅返回当前状态，不重复推进处理。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN；文档不存在 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_NOT_FOUND；当前用户不是上传者 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_PERMISSION_DENIED；存储状态查询失败 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_STORAGE_STATUS_GET_FAILED。\n- 响应：返回刷新后的文档状态。\n",
        "operationId": "syncDocStatus",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "documentId",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RDocumentStatus"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/document/retryDocProcess": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["文档处理"],
        "summary": "重试文档处理",
        "description": "- 用途：让上传者重新推进失败或资源注册超时的文档处理任务。\n- 请求：documentId 指定待重试文档。\n- 约束：当前用户必须是该文档上传者；文档状态只能是 FAILED 或 REGISTERING_RES_TIMEOUT。\n- 处理：FAILED 状态会重置为 UPLOADED 并重新发布解析任务；REGISTERING_RES_TIMEOUT 状态会重新执行资源注册完成流程；不重新申请上传 URL，不重新上传源文件。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN；文档不存在 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_NOT_FOUND；当前用户不是上传者 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_PERMISSION_DENIED；文档状态不允许重试 -> DocumentError.CANNOT_RETRY_DOCUMENT_PROCESS_IN_CURRENT_STATE；资源注册失败 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_REGISTER_RESOURCE_FAILED。\n- 响应：成功时返回空结果。\n",
        "operationId": "retryDocProcess",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "documentId",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RVoid"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/document/cancelDocProcess": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["文档处理"],
        "summary": "取消文档处理",
        "description": "- 用途：上传者取消未完成的文档上传或处理任务。\n- 请求：documentId 指定待取消文档。\n- 约束：当前用户必须是该文档上传者；READY 状态文档不能取消；CONVERTING_AND_PARSING 状态当前不允许取消。\n- 处理：删除文档信息、解析内容和 PDF 元数据记录，并发布相关对象存储文件删除事件；不删除已经注册为资源且处于 READY 的文档。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN；文档不存在 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_NOT_FOUND；当前用户不是上传者 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_PERMISSION_DENIED；READY 文档不允许取消 -> DocumentError.CANNOT_CANCEL_READY_DOCUMENT_PROCESS；当前状态不允许取消 -> DocumentError.CANNOT_CANCEL_DOCUMENT_PROCESS_IN_CURRENT_STATE。\n- 响应：成功时返回空结果。\n",
        "operationId": "cancelDocProcess",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "documentId",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RVoid"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/document/listPendingDocs": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["文档处理"],
        "summary": "查询未就绪文档",
        "description": "- 用途：查询当前用户仍处于上传、转换、解析或失败状态的文档任务。\n- 请求：无显式请求参数，上传者来自当前登录上下文。\n- 约束：当前用户必须已登录。\n- 处理：按当前用户筛选 UPLOADING、UPLOADED、TRANSFER_TIMEOUT、CONVERTING_AND_PARSING 和 FAILED 状态的文档；不刷新存储状态，也不触发重试。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN。\n- 响应：返回未就绪文档基础信息列表。\n",
        "operationId": "listPendingDocs",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RListDocumentInfoBase"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/document/getDocPreview": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["文档处理"],
        "summary": "获取文档预览",
        "description": "- 用途：为有查看权限的用户输出文档 PDF 预览流。\n- 请求：resourceId 指定文档资源；Range 请求头可用于分段读取。\n- 约束：当前用户必须已登录，且必须是资源所有者或拥有 VIEW 动作；文档必须已经处理完成并具备预览文件。\n- 处理：先通过资源服务校验权限，再读取文档预览元数据和对象存储下载地址；支持全量或 Range 响应，并在预览流尾部追加水印附录；不修改文档内容或资源权限。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN；资源无查看权限 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_PERMISSION_DENIED；文档不存在 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_NOT_FOUND；预览未就绪 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_PREVIEW_NOT_READY；预览元数据缺失或响应流写入失败 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_PREVIEW_FAILED。\n- 响应：直接写出 application/pdf 预览流。\n",
        "operationId": "previewDocument",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "resourceId",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK"
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/document/getDocInfo": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["文档处理"],
        "summary": "获取文档信息",
        "description": "- 用途：获取文档资源详情和文档处理信息，用于文档详情页展示。\n- 请求：resourceId 指定文档资源。\n- 约束：当前用户必须已登录，且必须通过资源服务的资源详情权限校验；目标文档信息必须存在。\n- 处理：通过资源服务获取资源详情和当前用户可执行动作，再读取文档信息并组合响应；不刷新文档状态，不触发解析或重试。\n- 失败：未登录 -> PermissionError.NOT_LOGIN；资源不存在 -> ResourceError.RESOURCE_NOT_FOUND；资源无查看权限 -> ResourceError.RESOURCE_PERMISSION_DENIED；文档不存在 -> DocumentError.DOCUMENT_NOT_FOUND。\n- 响应：返回资源信息与文档信息组合结果。\n",
        "operationId": "getNoteInfo",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "resourceId",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "OK",
            "content": {
              "*/*": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RDocumentInfoResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "FromSource": [],
            "UserID": [],
            "IdentityType": [],
            "GroupRoleMap": []
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "schemas": {
      "DocumentUploadInitRequest": {
        "required": ["expectedSize", "extension", "filename", "md5"],
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "filename": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "extension": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "md5": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "expectedSize": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          }
        }
      },
      "DocumentUploadInitResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "documentId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "putUrl": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "callbackHeader": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "objectKey": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "flashUploaded": {
            "type": "boolean"
          }
        }
      },
      "RDocumentUploadInitResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "key": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "msg": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "data": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentUploadInitResponse"
          }
        }
      },
      "DocumentStatus": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "UPLOADING",
              "UPLOADED",
              "CONVERTING_AND_PARSING",
              "REGISTERING_RES",
              "READY",
              "TRANSFER_TIMEOUT",
              "REGISTERING_RES_TIMEOUT",
              "FAILED"
            ]
          },
          "errorMessage": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "RDocumentStatus": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "key": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "msg": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "data": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentStatus"
          }
        }
      },
      "RVoid": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "key": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "msg": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object"
          }
        }
      },
      "DocumentInfoBase": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "uploadMeta": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentUploadMeta"
          },
          "documentStatus": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentStatus"
          },
          "maxPreviewPages": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          }
        }
      },
      "DocumentUploadMeta": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "documentName": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "uploaderId": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          },
          "fileType": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "NOTE",
              "PDF",
              "DOC",
              "DOCX",
              "PPT",
              "PPTX",
              "XLS",
              "XLSX",
              "SKILL",
              "AGENT",
              "UNKNOWN"
            ]
          },
          "size": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          }
        }
      },
      "RListDocumentInfoBase": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "key": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "msg": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentInfoBase"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "DocumentInfoResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "resourceInfo": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ResourceItemResponse"
          },
          "documentInfo": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentInfoBase"
          }
        }
      },
      "RDocumentInfoResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "key": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "msg": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "data": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DocumentInfoResponse"
          }
        }
      },
      "ResourceInteractionInfoBase": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "readCount": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "likeCount": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "scoreCount": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          },
          "scoreTotal": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int32"
          }
        }
      },
      "ResourceItemResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "resourceName": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "resourceType": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "NOTE",
              "PDF",
              "DOC",
              "DOCX",
              "PPT",
              "PPTX",
              "XLS",
              "XLSX",
              "SKILL",
              "AGENT",
              "UNKNOWN"
            ]
          },
          "ownerId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "preview": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "size": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64"
          },
          "resourceId": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "ownerInfo": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/UserDisplayBase"
          },
          "resourceInteractionInfo": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ResourceInteractionInfoBase"
          },
          "currentTags": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          "currentActions": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": ["DISCOVER", "VIEW", "EDIT", "DOWNLOAD_WATERMARK", "DOWNLOAD_ORIGINAL"]
            }
          },
          "overrideGrantedActions": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": ["DISCOVER", "VIEW", "EDIT", "DOWNLOAD_WATERMARK", "DOWNLOAD_ORIGINAL"]
            }
          },
          "specifiedUsersGrantedActions": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": ["DISCOVER", "VIEW", "EDIT", "DOWNLOAD_WATERMARK", "DOWNLOAD_ORIGINAL"]
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "UserDisplayBase": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "nickname": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "realName": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "avatar": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "identityType": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["1", "2", "3"]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "securitySchemes": {
      "FromSource": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "内部来源校验头。直连微服务测试时填写 APISIX 注入的固定来源值。",
        "name": "X-From-Source",
        "in": "header"
      },
      "UserID": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "当前用户 ID。直连微服务测试 @CheckLogin 接口时手工模拟 APISIX 注入。",
        "name": "X-User-Id",
        "in": "header"
      },
      "IdentityType": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "当前用户身份类型：1=学生，2=教师，3=管理员。",
        "name": "X-Identity-Type",
        "in": "header"
      },
      "GroupRoleMap": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "description": "当前用户小组角色 JSON，例如 {\"10001\":0}，角色值：0=OWNER，1=ADMIN，2=MEMBER。",
        "name": "X-Group-Role-Map",
        "in": "header"
      }
    }
  }
}
